# Graph Traversal Project Notes

## Objective
The purpose of this project was to implement graph traversal algorithms and visualize graph relationships using Java.

## BFS Analysis
Breadth-First Search traverses graph nodes level by level using a queue structure.

## DFS Analysis
Depth-First Search traverses nodes by exploring as far as possible before backtracking.

## Skills Demonstrated
- Java Programming
- Graph Data Structures
- BFS and DFS Algorithms
- Problem Solving
- Debugging

## What I Learned
This project strengthened my understanding of graph theory, algorithm implementation, and data structure behavior.
